<div id='banner'>
	<h1>Tic-Tac-Toe</h1>
</div>

<p>Welcome to Tic-Tac-Toe! This is a two player game. Each player takes turns marking X or O in one of the boxes on the game board until one player has three in a row (horizontally, vertically, or diagonally) or until there are no more availalbe moves. You can undo moves during your game and view replays of your previous games.<br>Good luck!</p>

<div id='game-header'>
	<button id='new-game-button'>New Game</button>
	<div id='current-player-container'>
		<h3>Current Player:</h3>
		<h1 id='current-player'></h1>
	</div>
	<button id='undo-button'>Undo</button>
</div>

<div id='game-board'>
	<div class='row'>
		<div class='cell player-0' id='0-0'></div>
		<div class='cell player-0' id='0-1'></div>
		<div class='cell player-0' id='0-2'></div>
	</div>
	<div class='row'>
		<div class='cell player-0' id='1-0'></div>
		<div class='cell player-0' id='1-1'></div>
		<div class='cell player-0' id='1-2'></div>
	</div>
	<div class='row'>
		<div class='cell player-0' id='2-0'></div>
		<div class='cell player-0' id='2-1'></div>
		<div class='cell player-0' id='2-2'></div>
	</div>
</div>

<div id='game-footer'>
	<h3>Previous Game Replays:</h3>
	<div id="replays-container"></div>
</div>

<div id='game-end-modal'>
	<div id='modal-content-container'>
		<h1 id='modal-content'></h1>
		<button id='modal-button'>Continue</button>
	</div>
</div>
